# id: AbstractPartitionDiscovererTest -> private static int getExpectedSubtaskIndex(KafkaTopicPartition partition, int startIndex, int numSubtasks)
commentText:
Utility method that determines the expected subtask index a partition should be assigned to,_depending on the start index and using the partition id as the offset from that start index_in clockwise direction.__

The expectation is based on the distribution contract of_{@link KafkaTopicPartitionAssigner#assign(KafkaTopicPartition, int)}.
codeText: private static int getExpectedSubtaskIndex(KafkaTopicPartition partition, int startIndex, int numSubtasks) {_		return (startIndex + partition.getPartition()) % numSubtasks__	}
